      "result": "\n\nThe `.claude/` directory **does not exist** in `/Volumes/T9/Code/projects/Project-Camiel/`.The find scan confirms — no `.claude` directory exists under `Project-Camiel`. Other projects in the workspace do have one (e.g. `athena`, `hermesv3`, `pan-agent`, etc.), but `Project-Camiel` itself has no such directory.\n\nWould you like me to create one, or explore a different location?"
